967
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:06,880
 Bog vam želi dati nove izljave duha svijetom.

968
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,480
 On ima puno,

969
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,940
 on ima u izobilju

