00:35:09,940 --> 00:35:11,860
 i on jedva čeka dati još.

971
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:14,440
 pitanje je želite li vi još.

972
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:17,440
 U dijelima dva oni doželjaju pedesetnicu.

973
