976
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:26,980
 Dijela četiri,

977
00:35:26,980 --> 00:35:29,240
 događa se nova pedesetnica,

978
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:31,380
 zove mala pedesetnica,

979
00:35:31,380 --> 00:35:35,480
 Petar i Ivan su ozdravili onog uzetog,

980
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:37,980
 crkvene vlasti,

981
