984
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:45,340
 pokušali ih priplašiti,

985
00:35:46,060 --> 00:35:47,980
 ono obećali im praktički progone

986
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:49,800
 i oni kažu,

987
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,640
