988
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:53,100
 Važnije je udovoljiti Bogu nego vama.

989
00:35:53,100 --> 00:35:55,420
 I nas ne zanima što vi mislite.

990
00:35:55,420 --> 00:35:57,160
 Mi samo želimo vršiti volju Božju.

991
00:35:57,160 --> 00:35:58,580
 Sad to malo sve karikiram.

992
00:35:58,580 --> 00:36:01,520
 I oni ih opomenu pošaljuća,

993
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:04,400
 Petar i Ivan se vraćaju u zajednicu vjernika,

994
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:05,560
