1002
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,860
 Da vidiš kako je to utjecalo na ljude.

1003
00:36:21,860 --> 00:36:23,000
 I onda su ovi čuli,

1004
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:23,800
 onda su nas uhvatili,

1005
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:24,800
 pa smo išli pred sud,

1006
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:26,220
 pa su nam sudili,

1007
00:36:26,220 --> 00:36:28,240
 pa smo se mi hrabro zauzeli.

1008
00:36:28,240 --> 00:36:29,820
 Imamo sad novu snagu u sebi

1009
00:36:29,820 --> 00:36:30,840
 poslije pedesetnice.

1010
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:33,240
 Je ona sad tu o ime meni,

1011
00:36:33,240 --> 00:36:33,540
 wow,

1012
00:36:33,540 --> 00:36:34,740
 i oni svi u deliriju.

1013
00:36:34,740 --> 00:36:35,960
 Zahvaljuju Bogu

1014
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:36,820
 i znate šta rade?

1015
00:36:36,820 --> 00:36:38,200
 Mole za još.

1016
00:36:38,200 --> 00:36:41,100
 I znate šta Bog radi?

1017
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:42,180
 Da je još.

1018
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:45,160
 Događa se novi izljev duha svetog.

1019
00:36:45,160 --> 00:36:48,240
 A znate za što su molili?

