1022
00:36:51,560 --> 00:36:52,420
 nova ozdravljenja

1023
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:53,480
 i nova oslobođenja.

1024
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:56,360
 I Bog opet prodrma mjesto

1025
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:58,300
 i svi se ispune duha svetog.

1026
00:36:58,300 --> 00:37:00,800
 Jesu već bili puni duha svetog

1027
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:01,400
 u dijelima dva?

1028
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:03,040
 Pa kako je moguće

1029
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:04,440
 da im opet želi da duha svetog?

1030
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:06,100
 Zato jer Bog ima još.

1031
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:07,680
 Ne postoji neka razina

1032
00:37:07,680 --> 00:37:08,960
 koju ćeš doseći

1033
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:10,320
