1038
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:15,560
 to je najbolje šta ja mogu,

1039
00:37:15,560 --> 00:37:17,140
 meni ne treba više ništa,

1040
00:37:17,140 --> 00:37:18,280
 ja samo idem sa svojim.

1041
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:18,580
 Ne.

1042
00:37:18,580 --> 00:37:20,880
 Bog nema maksimum.

1043
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:23,240
 Kad vidite živote svetaca

1044
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:23,900
 koji su uspjeli,

1045
00:37:23,900 --> 00:37:25,240
 nema maksimuma.

1046
00:37:25,240 --> 00:37:27,040
 Idu ekstaze

1047
00:37:27,040 --> 00:37:27,560
 i mole Boga

1048
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:28,840
 da im se tijelo ne raspadne

1049
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,660
 od ljubavi,

1050
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:30,660
 od prožvetosti,

1051
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:32,060
 svetošću Božom

1052
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:33,220
 i njegovom ljubavom.

1053
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,640
 Ne postoji maksimum.

1054
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:35,940
 Bog zna

1055
00:37:35,940 --> 00:37:36,860
 što mi možemo

