00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:39,020
 I uvijek ima još.

1058
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:40,020
 Božja ljubav

1059
00:37:40,020 --> 00:37:40,740
 i pedagogija

1060
00:37:40,740 --> 00:37:41,580
 uvijek rastućena.

1061
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:45,800
 Jel vam to radosna vijest?

1062
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:48,140
 Ne izgledate tako?

1063
00:37:48,140 --> 00:37:49,860
 Valjda je ovih puno

1064
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:50,820
