1065
00:37:50,820 --> 00:37:52,600
 još na vama stoji.

1066
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:53,680
 Stresite to sa sve

1067
00:37:53,680 --> 00:37:54,660
 idu radosne vijesti.

1068
00:37:54,660 --> 00:37:56,360
 Uglavnom,

1069
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,300
 Isus nije umrao

1070
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:58,260
 za nemoćnu crkvu.

1071
