1073
00:38:00,980 --> 00:38:01,600
 za svoju djetu,

1074
00:38:01,600 --> 00:38:02,440
 svoju obitelj,

1075
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:03,760
 da se pomućite,

1076
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,820
 napravite sve za njih

1077
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:05,860
 i oni na to ostaje.

1078
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:09,160
 Bija tamo

1079
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:09,640
 jedan dedo,

1080
00:38:09,640 --> 00:38:10,380
 dobar čovjek,

1081
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:12,200
 sve nam omoguća,

1082
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:13,420
 bezveza lik,

1083
00:38:13,420 --> 00:38:14,220
 ništa posebno.

1084
00:38:14,220 --> 00:38:16,240
 Tako se mi ponašamo

1085
00:38:16,240 --> 00:38:17,660
 malo prema Isusu.

1086
00:38:17,660 --> 00:38:21,900
 Što se tiče

1087
00:38:21,900 --> 00:38:22,940
 znakova znamenja

1088
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:23,520
 i čudesa

1089
00:38:23,520 --> 00:38:24,280
 o kojim pričam

1090
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,820
 i služba ozradljanja

1091
00:38:25,820 --> 00:38:26,460
 spada u to.

1092
00:38:26,460 --> 00:38:28,860
 To nije cjelovito

1093
00:38:28,860 --> 00:38:29,480
 evanđelje.

1094
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:31,260
 To je jedan dio

1095
00:38:31,260 --> 00:38:31,840
 evanđelja,

1096
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:32,800
 ali evanđelje

1097
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:33,540
 bez toga

1098
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,440
 nije cjelovito.

1099
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:36,060
 I navješta se,

1100
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:36,440
 nažalost.

1101
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,160
 Ja sam jučer bio

1102
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,200
 na jednoj župnoj misi

1103
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:39,300
 i učer ste čuli

1104
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:40,380
 prekrasna čitanja.

1105
00:38:40,380 --> 00:38:42,360
 Full karizmatska čitanja

1106
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:43,340
 o poslanju,

1107
00:38:43,340 --> 00:38:43,980
 o službama,

1108
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:45,160
 o tijelu Kristovo,

1109
00:38:45,160 --> 00:38:46,140
 o lječenja,

1110
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:47,160
 o oslobađanje.

1111
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,920
 Čuva sam,

1112
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:49,520
 pitao sam onda

1113
00:38:49,520 --> 00:38:50,400
 još neke prijatelje

1114
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,160
 koji se bili na drugim

1115
00:38:51,160 --> 00:38:52,400
 i samo i drugim crkvama,

1116
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:54,760
 niko ne navješta

1117
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,400
 to što piše.

1118
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:59,180
 Uzmu neke druge misle.

1119
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:02,460
 Jeste to primijetili?

1120
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:04,240
 Kako je skriveno ovo?

1121
00:39:04,240 --> 00:39:05,780
 A znate zašto?

1122
00:39:05,780 --> 00:39:07,000
 Očito je kolektivna

1123
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:07,700
 oholost

1124
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:08,680
 nas zaslijepila.

1125
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:10,760
 Kolektivna nevjera.

1126
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:14,620
 I Bog to želi promijeniti.

1127
00:39:14,620 --> 00:39:18,820
 Znači, ne možemo uzeti

1128
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:20,180
 evanđelje i nauk crkve

1129
00:39:20,180 --> 00:39:21,840
 i gledati to kao švedski stol.

1130
00:39:21,840 --> 00:39:22,760
 Meni je ovo, meni je ovo.

1131
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,920
 Bog će ti reći

1132
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:24,620
 šta je za tebe,

1133
00:39:24,620 --> 00:39:25,440
 koji je tvoj put.

1134
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:27,080
 Možda neće biti

1135
00:39:27,080 --> 00:39:28,120
 izrazano karizmatski.

1136
00:39:28,120 --> 00:39:29,320
 Možda će biti skrović život.

1137
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:31,220
 Možda će neko se zatvoriti

1138
00:39:31,220 --> 00:39:32,300
 u klauzarni samostan.

1139
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:34,060
 Ali taj život s Isusom

1140
00:39:34,060 --> 00:39:34,780
 je bogat.

1141
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:36,580
 On je dinamičan.

1142
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:38,240
 On je nevjerovatan.

1143
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,340
 On je viv.

1144
00:39:39,340 --> 00:39:43,980
 Ozdravljenja su bili

1145
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:45,400
 sastavni dio prve crkve.

1146
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:47,440
 Vidimo Isusov život

1147
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:49,040
 puno zdravljenja i oslobođenja.

1148
00:39:49,040 --> 00:39:50,260
 Onda vidimo dijela apostolska

1149
00:39:50,260 --> 00:39:51,400
 i prvu crkvu puna.

1150
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:53,240
 Ozdravljenja su sastavni dio.

1151
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:54,840
 Oni nisu neka sporedna stvar,

1152
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,700
 neka sekundarna stvar.

1153
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:58,220
 Oni su sastavni dio

1154
00:39:58,220 --> 00:39:59,680
 prve crkve.

1155
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:03,340
 moja osobno želja

1156
00:40:03,340 --> 00:40:04,640
 je da to postane

1157
00:40:04,640 --> 00:40:05,520
 i u naše vrijeme,

1158
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:06,100
 to sam vam rekao,

1159
00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:07,240
 da to postane norma.

1160
00:40:07,240 --> 00:40:08,660
 I kako ćete

1161
00:40:08,660 --> 00:40:11,840
 znati da ste vi zato?

1162
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:13,980
 Riječ Bože nam to kaže.

1163
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:16,740
 Kogod je kršten i kogod uzvjerov Isusa,

1164
00:40:16,740 --> 00:40:17,980
 on je kvalificira.

1165
00:40:17,980 --> 00:40:20,400
 To je sve što se traži.

1166
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,740
 Isus je rekao

1167
00:40:21,740 --> 00:40:27,280
 da ćemo raditi veće stvari od njega.

1168
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:29,140
 Drugim riječima,

1169
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:30,860
 radit ćete isto što i ja radim,

1170
00:40:30,860 --> 00:40:33,020
 a vi ćete raditi još i veće stvari od mene.

1171
00:40:33,700 --> 00:40:35,160
 On je na zemlji bio samo jedan

1172
00:40:35,160 --> 00:40:36,540
 i onda odšao u nebo

1173
00:40:36,540 --> 00:40:37,700
 da može po duhu svetom

1174
00:40:37,700 --> 00:40:39,160
 biti prisutan u svima nama.

1175
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:40,880
 Nas je sad milijardu i nešto.

1176
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:43,360
 Znate koja bi mi trebali svi skupa,

1177
00:40:43,360 --> 00:40:45,200
 to je s to on po nama radi stvari.

1178
00:40:45,200 --> 00:40:46,020
 On se multiplicirao.

1179
00:40:46,020 --> 00:40:48,220
 Koliko tabernakula

1180
00:40:48,220 --> 00:40:49,300
 postoji diljem svijeta.

1181
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,680
 Isus živi u tebi po duhu svetom.

1182
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:56,100
 Ista sila duha svetom

1183
00:40:56,100 --> 00:40:56,980
 koja je bila u Isusu

1184
00:40:56,980 --> 00:40:59,000
 i uskresnula Isusa od mrtvih je i u tebi.

1185
00:40:59,000 --> 00:40:59,520
 Ista sila.

1186
00:40:59,520 --> 00:41:01,480
 Nije duh sveti u meni slabiji

1187
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:02,820
 od duha svetom koji je u Isusu.

1188
00:41:02,820 --> 00:41:05,380
 Nije duh sveti raskomadan.

1189
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:09,140
 Ne zna, ne postoji ih milijardu duha svetom.

1190
00:41:09,140 --> 00:41:09,720
 Jedan je.

1191
00:41:09,720 --> 00:41:10,960
 Isti je u meni,

1192
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:12,600
 isti je u vama,

1193
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:13,700
 isti je u Isusu.

1194
00:41:13,700 --> 00:41:15,720
 Ista snaga,

1195
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:17,440
 ista osoba,

1196
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:21,160
 božanska osoba koja može sve.

1197
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,420
 je u vama.

1198
00:41:22,420 --> 00:41:23,720
 Wow.

1199
00:41:23,720 --> 00:41:25,180
 Wow.

1200
00:41:25,180 --> 00:41:26,600
 Može sve.

1201
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:28,220
 I kaže Isus,

1202
00:41:28,220 --> 00:41:29,320
 ako povjerujete u mene,

1203
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,800
 radit ćete i veće stvari

1204
00:41:30,800 --> 00:41:31,980
 nego što ih ja radim.

1205
00:41:31,980 --> 00:41:33,000
 A Isus,

1206
